getInternalLicenseConflicts

public java.util.ArrayList<Pair<License,License>> getInternalLicenseConflicts(FileID file)
Get the list of license conflicts inside a file. A license pair is returned for each conflicting pair of licenses. If licenses a and b conflict with each other, both pairs (a, b) and (b, a) are returned.

Parameters:

Returns:
List of license conflicts found inside the given file

getGlobalLicenseConflicts

public java.util.ArrayList<Pair<License,License>> getGlobalLicenseConflicts()
Return found global license conflicts. A license pair is returned for each conflicting pair of licenses. If licenses a and b conflict with each other, both pairs (a, b) and (b, a) are returned.

Returns:
List of conflicts between any/all found licenses

processPackage

public void processPackage()
Runs all processing steps for the package.
  • Sort files to source files,license files and unknown files
  • Scan source files
  • Scan license files
  • Determine references
  • Determine license conflicts

    • processFoundLicenses

    private void processFoundLicenses()

    private void processFoundReferences()

    findLicenseConflicts

    private void findLicenseConflicts()
    Scans the licenseMatches and references, finds any conflicts. Licenses found in source files are compared with other licenses found in the same and referenced source files. Licenses found in license files are compared only with other licenses found in the same file Also all found licenses are checked for conflicts with any other found licenses.
